  "description": "Decoration addon for Just Stargate Mod",
  "body": "<!-- Shields - versions, discord etc. -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jsg-addon-rings/files/all\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/for_MC-1.20.1-orange\" alt=\"Minecraft Versions\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.justsgmod.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/881802052488011837?style=flat-square&label= &logo=discord&color=2D2D2D\" alt=\"Discord invite\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jsg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/-JustStargateMod-2d2d2d?style=flat-square&logo=Pinboard&logoColor=3c85e6\" alt=\"JSG\"/></a></p>\n\n<!-- Main banner with current version of 1.20.1 -->\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/Fredyman95/Repository-of-knowledge/blob/main/cf/decor.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Decor Addon\"/>\n\n<!-- Warning JSg is needed -->\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <th>\n      <h2><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\"><strong>IMPORTANT</strong></p></h2>\n    </th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <th>\n      <p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jsg\">Just Stargate Mod (JSG) is a mandatory dependency for mod. This addon must be paired with Just Stargate Mod (JSG) version 5.1.0.0 or higher.</a></p>\n    </th>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<!-- Minedragon Bust and text -->\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <td width=\"30%\"> \n      <p><img src=\"https://vzge.me/bust/700/171b6e4003d641feac5aa31658de6832.png\"></p> \n    </td>\n    <td></td>\n    <td width=\"70%\">\n        <h2><strong>More then Decoration</strong></h2><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:left\">Elevate your world with the next official expansion from the TauriDev team. This addon introduces decorative blocks and specialized features designed to complement the core JSG experience. Beyond unique Stargate aesthetics, it seamlessly extends the vanilla palette with custom trapdoors, doors, and boats—bridging the gap between Stargate technology and classic Minecraft design.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- Fredyman Bust and text -->\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <td width=\"70%\">\n      <h2><strong>Building Palette</strong></h2><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:left\">This is only the beginning. Future updates will transcend basic block palettes -  specialized structural blocks designed for cinematic accuracy. Whether you are recreating the corridors of the SGC, high-tech Atlantis city, or the ancient spaceship Destiny, our addon provides the essential blocks. This is your foundation for building the most iconic locations from Stargate series.</p>\n    </td>\n    <td></td>\n    <td width=\"30%\"> \n      <p><img src=\"https://vzge.me/bust/700/b9889cd78c4d4b3385bd2c1415363f17.png?y=-40\"></p> \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- Trailer-->\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/955/122/trailer.png\" alt=\"Trailer\"/>\n<span><iframe width=\"1000\" height=\"560\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SeZOdZswP_Q\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></span>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- Support-->\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/956/70/support.png\" alt=\"Support Us\"/>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=ZYD4K634P5HQU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/956/53/pp.png\" alt=\"paypal button\"/></a></p>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- Other projects table -->\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/tauri-development\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/955/959/otherprojects.png\"></a></p>\n\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/jsg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/1039/875/638565645126910597.png\"></p>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/jsg-addon-rings\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1241/674/256/256/638812183885157132.png\"></p> \n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/jsg-addon-destiny\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1606/775/256/256/639037353864534454.png\"></p> \n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rsj\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/955/930/logo.png\"></p> \n      </a>\n    </th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <th>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/jsg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">Just Stargate Mod</p></strong>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/jsg-addon-rings\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">Transport rings addon</p></strong>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/jsg-addon-destiny\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">Destiny addon</p></strong>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rsj\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">Redstone Jukeboxes</p></strong>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n  </tr>\n</table>",
